    "description": "《三国群英传M》以忠实还原《三国群英传Online》为目标，掌握原始美术风格、职业、打宝吃王、武魂、国战等核心玩法，让老玩家能随时随地重怀过往三国旅程。<br><br>【游戏特色】<br>■ 延续三国经典唤回你的热血感动<br>超过百张地图还原线上游戏世界，知名历史武魂再现三国群英，经典横向卷轴玩法，体验的不只是最初的回忆，还有热血与感动。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321430/extras/2ab8bdb01c2fd38d4869a25ac44ab6b5.poster.avif?t=1743404645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321430/extras/2ab8bdb01c2fd38d4869a25ac44ab6b5.webm?t=1743404645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321430/extras/2ab8bdb01c2fd38d4869a25ac44ab6b5.mp4?t=1743404645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>■ 畅玩三群一手掌握<br>跨世代操作，打破电脑设备和环境等因素，实现全民皆兵的目标。<br><br>■ 千军万马尽在掌中<br>透过不同的兵种配置应付不同的战况，玩法变化多元，超越游戏的特别体验<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321430/extras/c06a96f3d70185f9d838935550bc1a65.poster.avif?t=1743404645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321430/extras/c06a96f3d70185f9d838935550bc1a65.webm?t=1743404645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321430/extras/c06a96f3d70185f9d838935550bc1a65.mp4?t=1743404645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>■ 全区指挥热血参战<br>「指挥系统」全区掌控，不需要语音和打字沟通即可让军团长快速掌握战局，决战千里之外。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321430/extras/c7844ce53bac451566b8039432bf0627.poster.avif?t=1743404645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321430/extras/c7844ce53bac451566b8039432bf0627.webm?t=1743404645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321430/extras/c7844ce53bac451566b8039432bf0627.mp4?t=1743404645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>■ 自动挂机线上竞标<br>超高自由度的竞标系统，体现自给自足的自由经济；最完善的挂机功能，享受最佳「打宝」乐趣。<br><br>■ 百炼战甲神兵锻造<br>解放装备限制，简化强化需求，只要有心，每件装备都会成为神之兵器。<br><br>■ 武魂重现万人国战<br>化身三国名将，小卒也能成英雄；实现万人国战，打造国战最佳体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321430/extras/b26558c59556f76b3edef6132b188e4f.poster.avif?t=1743404645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321430/extras/b26558c59556f76b3edef6132b188e4f.webm?t=1743404645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321430/extras/b26558c59556f76b3edef6132b188e4f.mp4?t=1743404645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>■ 三国名将尽在指间<br>化身三国名将，与同伴一起征战沙场，亲临古战场，感受名场面<br><br>抵制不良游戏，拒绝盗版游戏。<br>注意自我保护，谨防受骗上当。<br>适度游戏益脑，沉迷游戏伤身。<br>合理安排时间，享受健康生活。<br>©USERJOY Technology Co., Ltd. All Rights Reserved.",
